<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/284910-do-i-have-to-read-shadow-of-the-wind">Do I *have* to read Shadow of the Wind first? Or can I just read Angel&#39;s Game since it&#39;s a prequel?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_284910'><a id="like_count_community_question_284910" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/284910?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">9 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F4912857-the-angel-s-game">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/284910-do-i-have-to-read-shadow-of-the-wind">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/284910-do-i-have-to-read-shadow-of-the-wind">See all 7 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

